This paper deals with the problem of imbalanced classification, which is a common issue in machine learning. The proposed method involves modifying the entropy fuzzy support vector machine (EFSVM) to introduce instance-based entropy fuzzy support vector machine (IEFSVM). This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses numerical experiments on datasets, which suggests that it could also belong to computer vision (cs.CV) or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with the concept of entropy, which is a common topic in data mining (cs.DM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, and cs.DM.
